item.title: What's So Great About the Cloverfield Paradox?
item.description: [UPCOMING CHANGES: Some followers of Cloudnine have requested more main stream content, like movie reviews. We are working hard to bring you some of those changes. Thanks for your patience.] Nothing, but it could have been worse. Actually, I got bored and didn't watch it all. I'm writing about it here because there were a couple of things I liked. I'll tell you about those shortly. First, disclaimer: I didn't watch any of the Cloverfield series.
